 data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532311\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 28, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104tel1666854566665.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tel1666854566665.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/tel1666854566665.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"tel1666854566665\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Load Definitions functionality is supported for Sybase.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tel1666854566665__section_mw5_fyg_3vb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d400220e49\"> Functionality </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The Load Definitions facility for Sybase loads tables, views, columns, and\n\t\t\t\tindexes.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">It does not load relationships.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tel1666854566665__topic_d6692e1_d6693e1_d6694e1_d6695e1_d6696e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d400220e61\"> Configuration </h2>\n<div class=\"p\">Before loading definitions from Sybase:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"tel1666854566665__ul_jtm_fyz_hvb\">\n<li class=\"li\">Specify the SYB connector in the [DRIVERS] section of the IDE assignment\n\t\t\t\t\t\tfile.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">Define the $SYB path in the [PATHS] section of the IDE assignment file.</li>\n</ul></div>\n<p class=\"p\">For more detailed instructions, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"abg1665702623914.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/abg1665702623914.html\" title=\"For some databases, you can import the data dictionary definitions of an existing database into the application model using the Load Definitions facility, which is provided in Project Editor, in the Tables tab of the Resource Browser.\">Import Data Definitions From a DBMS</a></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"tel1666854566665__topic_d6697e1_d6698e1_d6699e1_d6700e1_d6701e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d400220e90\"> Data Type Mapping</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"tel1666854566665__p_d8756e1_d8757e1_d8758e1\">The Load Definitions utility maps Sybase data types to\n\t\t\t\tUniface data types and packing codes. The following table lists these mappings.</p>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><div class=\"dataTables_wrapper no-footer\" id=\"tel1666854566665__table_twl_3bh_3vb_wrapper\"><div class=\"dataTables_filter\" id=\"tel1666854566665__table_twl_3bh_3vb_filter\"><label>Search:<input aria-controls=\"tel1666854566665__table_twl_3bh_3vb\" class=\"\" placeholder=\"\" type=\"search\"/></label></div><div class=\"zDocsFilterTableDiv false\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Filter columns\" class=\"zDocsTopicPageColumnsButton dropdown-toggle\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\">Column<svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-filter\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-filter\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu\"><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Sybase Data Type-0-0\" id=\"topic-Sybase Data Type-0-0\" name=\"topic-Sybase Data Type-0-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Sybase Data Type-0-0\">Sybase Data Type</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Supported by Load Definitions-1-0\" id=\"topic-Supported by Load Definitions-1-0\" name=\"topic-Supported by Load Definitions-1-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Supported by Load Definitions-1-0\">Supported by Load Definitions</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Uniface Data Type-2-0\" id=\"topic-Uniface Data Type-2-0\" name=\"topic-Uniface Data Type-2-0\" type=\"checkbox\"/><label for=\"topic-Uniface Data Type-2-0\">Uniface Data Type</label></div><p class=\"dropdown-item\"></p><div class=\"zDocsCheckbox\"><input checked=\"\" data-testid=\"topic-Uni